data.description: Charming, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, updated home in the the established neighborhood of Hollywood. Located near interstate, beach, bases, and shopping. Single level ranch that sits on a large lot, with a huge detached garage/shed. Everything has been updated within the past several years including, flooring, kitchen, bathroom, windows, roof, and the HVAC is 2021. Truly turn key and move in ready.
